691
01:11:01,924 --> 01:11:05,257
Ili ljudski glas...

692
01:11:05,327 --> 01:11:07,261
pored našeg.

693
01:11:35,557 --> 01:11:37,718
Kuda ideš?

694
01:11:37,793 --> 01:11:41,490
- Do obeležja.
- Ah, da, veštica.

695
01:11:41,563 --> 01:11:45,397
Zašto je spaljivati nocu
kad je ljudima potrebno provodjenje?

696
01:11:45,467 --> 01:11:48,061
Ucuti, pobogu.

697
01:11:48,137 --> 01:11:50,833
Djavo je sa njom.

698
01:11:50,906 --> 01:11:53,397
Onda si ti osmi od hrabrih.

699
01:11:53,475 --> 01:11:57,536
Nismo placeni.
Ovo je volonterski posao.

700
01:13:36,211 --> 01:13:38,179
Cuješ li me?

701
01:13:40,048 --> 01:13:42,778
Kažu da trguješ sa djavolom.

702
01:13:42,851 --> 01:13:44,785
Zašto pitaš?

703
01:13:44,853 --> 01:13:48,345
Iz licnih razloga.

704
01:13:50,125 --> 01:13:52,457
I ja hocu da ga sretnem.

705
01:13:52,528 --> 01:13:54,359
Zašto?

706
01:13:55,664 --> 01:13:58,531
Moram da ga pitam za Boga.

707
01:13:58,600 --> 01:14:00,591
On sigurno zna.

708
01:14:04,039 --> 01:14:06,940
Možeš da ga vidiš bilo kad.

709
01:14:07,009 --> 01:14:08,476
Kako?

710
01:14:08,544 --> 01:14:10,910
Ako radiš šta ti ja kažem.

711
01:14:13,182 --> 01:14:15,082
Pogledaj me u oci.

712
01:14:17,953 --> 01:14:22,185
Vidiš li ga?

713
01:14:22,257 --> 01:14:25,954
Vidim užas.

714
01:14:26,028 --> 01:14:27,461
Ništa drugo.

715
01:14:31,233 --> 01:14:34,168
Ništa? Nikog?

716
01:14:36,572 --> 01:14:38,301
Ne.

717
01:14:40,008 --> 01:14:42,340
On nije iza tebe?

718
01:14:45,214 --> 01:14:48,547
Nema nikog.

719
01:14:52,287 --> 01:14:54,517
On je svuda sa mnom.

720
01:14:54,590 --> 01:14:58,287
Ako ogrebem ruku,
osetim ga.

721
01:14:58,360 --> 01:15:00,851
Cak i sada.

722
01:15:00,929 --> 01:15:02,897
Vatra me ne povredjuje.

723
01:15:02,965 --> 01:15:04,933
- Rekao je to?
- Ja znam.

724
01:15:05,000 --> 01:15:08,663
- A je li rekao to?
-Ja znam.Osecam.

725
01:15:08,737 --> 01:15:11,501
Mora da si ga i ti video.

726
01:15:11,573 --> 01:15:15,168
Sveštenici su ga videli,
i vojnici.

727
01:15:15,244 --> 01:15:18,407
Ne usudjuju se da me dodirnu.

728
01:15:24,753 --> 01:15:26,721
Zašto si joj slomio ruke?

729
01:15:26,788 --> 01:15:29,279
- Nismo mi.
- Ko?

730
01:15:29,358 --> 01:15:31,292
Pitaj onog monaha.

731
01:15:32,995 --> 01:15:35,520
Šta ste ucinili sa detetom?

732
01:15:40,569 --> 01:15:42,867
Hoceš li ikad prestati 
da zapitkuješ?

733
01:15:44,339 --> 01:15:48,366
Ne. Nikad.

734
01:15:48,443 --> 01:15:50,877
Ali ne dobijaš odgovor.

735
01:16:08,430 --> 01:16:11,422
Razmišljao sam o 
ubijanju vojnika...

736
01:16:11,500 --> 01:16:13,695
a ona je vec skoro mrtva.

737
01:16:13,769 --> 01:16:16,431
Rekao sam ti da paziš.
Ne prilazi joj.

738
01:16:27,983 --> 01:16:31,043
Ovo ce umiriti bol.

739
01:17:32,014 --> 01:17:35,074
Šta ona vidi?

740
01:17:35,150 --> 01:17:38,711
- Ona ne oseca bol.
- Nisi odgovorio.

741
01:17:38,787 --> 01:17:41,221
Ko ce se brinuti o detetu posle?

742
01:17:41,289 --> 01:17:45,020
Andjeli? Bog? Djavo?
Praznina?

743
01:17:46,128 --> 01:17:49,495
- Ne, praznina, gospodine!
- Ne može biti.

744
01:17:49,564 --> 01:17:50,997
Pogledaj joj u oci.

745
01:17:51,066 --> 01:17:54,558
Njen jadan um razotkriva.

746
01:17:54,636 --> 01:17:56,763
Praznina!

747
01:17:56,838 --> 01:17:58,669
Ne.

748
01:17:58,740 --> 01:18:01,402
Bespomocni smo.

749
01:18:01,476 --> 01:18:05,037
Vidimo što i ona vidi,
njen užas je i naš.

750
01:18:06,515 --> 01:18:08,983
Jadno dete!

751
01:18:09,051 --> 01:18:10,985
Ne mogu više!

752
01:19:26,695 --> 01:19:31,598
Peva tako divno
o Isusu Hristu

753
01:19:31,666 --> 01:19:35,762
na nebu je velika radost

754
01:19:38,306 --> 01:19:40,797
Uskoro ce sumrak...

755
01:19:40,876 --> 01:19:43,811
ali vrucina guši.

756
01:19:43,879 --> 01:19:47,542
Plašim se.

757
01:19:47,616 --> 01:19:49,914
Osecamo da ce nešto 
da nam se desi...

758
01:19:49,985 --> 01:19:53,011
Ali ne znamo šta.

759
01:19:53,088 --> 01:19:55,022
Sudnji dan, možda.

760
01:19:55,090 --> 01:19:56,682
Sudnji dan.

761
01:20:08,870 --> 01:20:10,667
Daj mi vode!

762
01:20:12,908 --> 01:20:14,603
Imam trbobolju.

763
01:20:14,676 --> 01:20:17,440
Budi na drugoj strani drveta.

764
01:20:23,485 --> 01:20:25,817
Plašim se smrti.

765
01:20:25,887 --> 01:20:29,118
Necu da umrem!

766
01:20:34,563 --> 01:20:36,997
Sažali se na mene.

767
01:20:39,534 --> 01:20:42,230
Pricaj sa mnom!

768
01:20:47,943 --> 01:20:49,877
Beskorisno je.

769
01:20:52,714 --> 01:20:54,875
Znam da jeste!

770
01:20:59,254 --> 01:21:01,415
Umirem.

771
01:21:06,528 --> 01:21:08,723
Šta ce biti sa mnom?

772
01:21:12,634 --> 01:21:14,795
Sažali se na mene.

773
01:21:18,607 --> 01:21:20,541
Jer nama pomoci?

774
01:21:23,178 --> 01:21:25,112
Besmisleno je.

775
01:21:28,016 --> 01:21:31,349
Krajnje besmisleno!

776
01:21:31,419 --> 01:21:33,080
Pomozi mi!

777
01:21:33,154 --> 01:21:35,384
Cuješ li? Tešim te.

778
01:22:01,983 --> 01:22:04,417
hocemo li da završimo našu igru?

779
01:22:05,220 --> 01:22:06,653
Tvoj potez!

780
01:22:14,863 --> 01:22:17,161
Uzimam ti kraljicu.

781
01:22:17,232 --> 01:22:19,097
Nisam to video.

782
01:22:34,749 --> 01:22:36,683
Vidim nešto grozno.

783
01:22:36,751 --> 01:22:39,379
- Nešto što ti teško mogu reci.
- Šta vidiš?

784
01:22:39,454 --> 01:22:42,582
Vitez igra šah ovde.

785
01:22:42,657 --> 01:22:45,217
To vidim. Šta s tim?

786
01:22:45,293 --> 01:22:47,227
Zar ne vidiš ko je drugi?

787
01:22:47,295 --> 01:22:50,196
On je sam.
Nemoj tako da me plašiš.

788
01:22:50,265 --> 01:22:53,996
- Ne, nije sam.
- Ko je sa njim?

789
01:22:54,069 --> 01:22:57,664
Igra šah sa smrcu.

790
01:22:58,406 --> 01:23:00,203
Ne smeš to da govoriš.

791
01:23:00,275 --> 01:23:03,938
- Moramo da bežimo.
- ne bez njega.

792
01:23:04,012 --> 01:23:08,676
Toliko su duboko u igri, 
da nece primetiti.

793
01:23:15,123 --> 01:23:18,092
Tvoj potez, Antonius Block.

794
01:23:22,130 --> 01:23:24,223
Jesi li izgubio interes?

795
01:23:27,736 --> 01:23:29,636
Naprotiv!

796
01:23:29,704 --> 01:23:32,798
Izgledaš zabrinut.

797
01:23:32,874 --> 01:23:35,502
Kriješ li nešto?

798
01:23:35,577 --> 01:23:37,977
Ništa ti ne promice.

799
01:23:38,046 --> 01:23:41,174
Ništa mi ne promice.

800
01:23:41,249 --> 01:23:43,342
Niko ti ne promice.

801
01:23:44,652 --> 01:23:46,643
Pitam se je li istina.

802
01:23:48,089 --> 01:23:50,023
Uplašen si.

803
01:23:58,099 --> 01:24:00,090
Zaboravio sam kako stajaše figure.

804
01:24:02,737 --> 01:24:04,796
Ali ja nisam.

805
01:24:06,307 --> 01:24:08,798
Ne možeš da se izvuceš tako lako!

806
01:24:17,585 --> 01:24:20,486
- Ah, vidim.
- Šta vidiš?

807
01:24:23,024 --> 01:24:25,185
Matiran si u sledecem potezu.

808
01:24:29,030 --> 01:24:30,327
Istina.

809
01:24:32,300 --> 01:24:34,291
Jesi li dobio na odlaganju?

810
01:24:34,369 --> 01:24:36,963
Jesam.

811
01:24:37,806 --> 01:24:40,934
Drago mi je.

812
01:24:41,009 --> 01:24:43,443
Kada se ponovo sretnemo...

813
01:24:43,511 --> 01:24:47,743
cas ce otkucati za tebe 
i tvoje prijatelje.

814
01:24:51,953 --> 01:24:54,012
I tvoje tajne ce se obelodaniti.

815
01:24:54,989 --> 01:24:57,014
Nemam tajni.

816
01:24:57,092 --> 01:25:00,220
Znaci ne znaš ništa?

817
01:25:01,129 --> 01:25:02,858
Ne znam.

818
01:25:26,154 --> 01:25:28,486
Kako cudno svetlo!

819
01:25:28,556 --> 01:25:31,457
Oluja sa grmljavinom.

820
01:25:31,526 --> 01:25:34,290
Ne. To je nešto užasno.

821
01:25:34,362 --> 01:25:36,296
Cuješ li grmljavinu?

822
01:25:36,364 --> 01:25:38,332
To je samo kiša.

823
01:25:40,835 --> 01:25:43,360
Ne. Video nas je.

824
01:25:43,438 --> 01:25:45,372
Progoni nas.

825
01:25:59,287 --> 01:26:01,881
Unutra, Mary! Brzo!

826
01:26:08,129 --> 01:26:10,723
Andjeo suda prelece...

827
01:26:10,798 --> 01:26:14,529
i strašno je veliki.

828
01:26:14,602 --> 01:26:16,536
Koliko je hladno!

829
01:28:20,194 --> 01:28:23,891
Cula sam kada si se vracao...

830
01:28:25,166 --> 01:28:27,225
pa sam te cekala.

831
01:28:27,302 --> 01:28:29,463
Ostali su pobegli od bolesti.

832
01:28:36,377 --> 01:28:38,902
Zar me ne poznaješ više?

833
01:28:43,651 --> 01:28:46,119
I ti si se promenio.

834
01:28:53,294 --> 01:28:55,762
Sad vidim da si to ti.

835
01:28:57,198 --> 01:29:00,167
Skriven duboko u ocima...

836
01:29:07,008 --> 01:29:11,308
decak koji je odavno otišao.

837
01:29:13,915 --> 01:29:18,318
Gotovo je sada, umoran sam.

838
01:29:18,386 --> 01:29:20,980
Zao ti je što si otišao?

839
01:29:21,055 --> 01:29:24,923
Ne. Ali umoran sam.

840
01:29:33,034 --> 01:29:34,968
To vidim.

841
01:29:43,144 --> 01:29:45,374
To su mi prijatelji.

842
01:29:48,282 --> 01:29:52,184
Pozovi ih unutra.
Pripremicu obrok.

843
01:29:57,458 --> 01:30:01,451
"I kada jagnje otvori sedmi pecat...

844
01:30:01,529 --> 01:30:05,795
"tišina zavlada nebom...

845
01:30:05,867 --> 01:30:08,836
"na pola casa.

846
01:30:10,138 --> 01:30:12,663
"i sedam Andjela...

847
01:30:12,740 --> 01:30:15,675
"koji držahu sedam truba...

848
01:30:15,743 --> 01:30:19,702
"pripremiše se da zatrube.

849
01:30:31,259 --> 01:30:35,696
"Zatrubi prvi andjeo,
i usledi...

850
01:30:35,763 --> 01:30:40,291
"buka i vatra pomešana sa krvlju...

851
01:30:40,368 --> 01:30:43,860
"i zavladaše zemljom.

852
01:30:48,843 --> 01:30:53,041
"I trecina šume izgore ...

853
01:30:54,182 --> 01:30:58,778
"i sva trava izgore.

854
01:30:58,853 --> 01:31:03,051
"I drugi andjeo zatrubi...

855
01:31:04,358 --> 01:31:08,727
"i velika planina izgore...

856
01:31:08,796 --> 01:31:11,856
"i nestade u moru.

857
01:31:11,933 --> 01:31:16,302
"I trecina mora postade krv."

858
01:31:16,370 --> 01:31:17,928
Ima li koga tamo?

859
01:31:23,611 --> 01:31:26,273
Ne, gospodine. Ne videh nikog.

860
01:31:30,418 --> 01:31:33,910
"I zatrubi treci andjeo...

861
01:31:36,691 --> 01:31:41,594
" i pade velika zvezda sa neba...

862
01:31:41,662 --> 01:31:45,621
"goreci kao svetiljka.

863
01:31:45,700 --> 01:31:50,535
"I ime te zvezde bejaše"Wormwood"."

864
01:32:26,274 --> 01:32:28,640
Dobro jutro, plemeniti gospodine.

865
01:32:30,278 --> 01:32:33,941
Ja sam Karin, vitezova žena...

866
01:32:34,015 --> 01:32:36,711
Dobrodošao u moju kucu.

867
01:32:38,486 --> 01:32:41,284
Ja sam kovac...

868
01:32:41,355 --> 01:32:44,347
i to dobar.

869
01:32:44,425 --> 01:32:47,451
Moja žena Lisa.

870
01:32:47,528 --> 01:32:50,156
Pokloni se gospodinu, Lisa.

871
01:32:51,732 --> 01:32:54,701
Vešte je ruke...

872
01:32:54,769 --> 01:32:58,569
a u svadji nismo gori od drugih .

873
01:32:59,907 --> 01:33:03,536
Izvan naše tame,
zovemo tebe, O Gospode!

874
01:33:03,611 --> 01:33:06,944
Oh, Bože, smiluj se na nas!

875
01:33:07,014 --> 01:33:10,506
mi smo mali i uplašeni
bez znanja.

876
01:33:10,585 --> 01:33:13,281
U tami
gde kažeš da jesi...

877
01:33:13,354 --> 01:33:18,155
nema nikoga da cuje 
tvoje jadikovajne.

878
01:33:21,195 --> 01:33:24,358
Odbio si se o svoju ravnodušnost.

879
01:33:24,432 --> 01:33:29,836
Bože, koji si negde,
mora te negde imati...

880
01:33:29,904 --> 01:33:32,099
smiluj se na nas!

881
01:33:32,173 --> 01:33:35,108
Mogao sam da ocistim tvoje 
brige o vecnosti...

882
01:33:35,176 --> 01:33:37,110
ali sada je kasno.

883
01:33:37,178 --> 01:33:42,206
Ali oseti, do kraja,
trijumf života!

884
01:33:42,283 --> 01:33:44,751
Tišina, tišina!

885
01:33:44,819 --> 01:33:47,811
Da, ali u izjavi.

886
01:34:09,343 --> 01:34:11,504
Došlo je vreme.

887
01:35:06,033 --> 01:35:08,194
Vidim ih, Mary!

888
01:35:10,071 --> 01:35:13,199
Tamo na olujnom nebu.

889
01:35:13,274 --> 01:35:15,469
Svi su tamo.

890
01:35:15,543 --> 01:35:18,011
Kovac i Lisa,
vitez...

891
01:35:18,079 --> 01:35:20,946
Raval, Jöns, i Skat.

892
01:35:21,015 --> 01:35:24,815
A strogi gospodar smrt
zapoveda im da plešu.

893
01:35:25,920 --> 01:35:28,616
Zapoveda da se drže za ruke...

894
01:35:28,689 --> 01:35:32,420
i da drže korak u dugoj liniji.

895
01:35:32,493 --> 01:35:34,654
Na celu je strogi gospodar...

896
01:35:34,729 --> 01:35:37,220
sa kamom i satom.

897
01:35:37,298 --> 01:35:40,756
A luda je poslednji sa lautom.

898
01:35:42,103 --> 01:35:46,437
Krecu se do sumraka...

899
01:35:46,507 --> 01:35:49,067
u svecanom plesu...

900
01:35:49,143 --> 01:35:52,044
prema mracnim zemljama...

901
01:35:52,113 --> 01:35:55,674
dok im kiša pere obraze...

902
01:35:55,750 --> 01:35:59,550
od soli gorkih suza.

903
01:36:03,691 --> 01:36:06,387
Ti sa tvojim vizijama!

904
01:36:28,349 --> 01:36:32,285
Preveo B. Krstic

